argin:0 0 24px 0;\">\r\n                                            Tip: choose a real target account. The difference is instant.\r\n                                        </p>\r\n\r\n                                        <p style=\"font-size:20px; line-height:32px; margin:0 0 32px 0;\">\r\n                                            Demo that look like you spent days. Ready in minutes.\r\n                                        </p>\r\n\r\n                                        <!-- Watch a Demo Button -->\r\n                                        <table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"margin:0 0 32px 0;\">\r\n                                            <tr>\r\n                                                <td align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#0E3A84\"\r\n                                                    style=\"width:174px; height:55px; border-radius:6px;\">\r\n                                                    <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bg8PDRuqMjk&t=2s\"\r\n                                                        style=\"display:inline-block; width:174px; height:55px; line-height:55px; font-size:20px; font-weight:500; color:#ffffff; text-decoration:none; text-align:center;\">\r\n                                                        Watch a demo\r\n                                                    </a>\r\n                                                </td>\r\n                                            </tr>\r\n                                        </table>\r\n\r\n                                        <p style=\"font-size:20px; line-height:32px; margin:0 0 24px 0;\">\r\n                                            Over the next week, we’ll drop some helpful tips with handy info on how to make the most of your time here.\r\n                                        </p>\r\n\r\n                                        <p style=\"font-size:20px; line-height:32px; margin:0 0 24px 0;\">\r\n                                            - <strong>The Blitz Team</strong>\r\n                                        </p>\r\n\r\n                                        <hr style=\"border:0; border-top:1px solid #D7DADD; margin:24px 0;\">\r\n\r\n                                        <p style=\"font-size:20px; line-height:32px; margin:0 0 24px 0;\">\r\n                                            We can’t wait to show you how effortless winning demos can be!\r\n                                        </p>\r\n\r\n                                        <!-- Explore + Social -->\r\n                                        <table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"\r\n                                            style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0;\">\r\n                                            <tr>\r\n                                                <td align=\"left\">\r\n                                                    <table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n                                                        <tr>\r\n                                                            <td align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#7D426E\"\r\n                                                                style=\"width:200px; height:40px; border-radius:4px;\">\r\n                                                                <a href=\"https://www.blitzdemos.ai/\"\r\n                                                                    style=\"display:inline-block; width:191px; height:40px; line-height:40px; font-size:16px; font-weight:bold; color:#ffffff; text-decoration:none; text-align:center;\">\r\n                                                                    Explore our website\r\n                                                                </a>\r\n                                                            </td>\r\n                                                        </tr>\r\n                                                    </table>\r\n                 